Subject: Re: [T2] '78 Top Bolt Rear Shocks....

The Bolt is 12mm x 1.5 Thread x 102mm Long.  12mm Bolts generally have 19mm
Hex Heads.

And just for reference the Bottom Bolt is 12mm x 1.5 Thread x 90mm Long.
